{"tid":1146572,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"「推至頂」旺角魚蛋革命...終結？","createTime":"2019-05-09T10:01:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-10T13:01:48.000Z","uid":66390,"like":19,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3b61e8eaf95b6763b2b2e5e1651e4e89b7e16a41","tid":1146572,"uid":66390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T10:01:57.000Z","msg":"我睇到呢條來自蘋果既片段<br />\n忍唔住喊左<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190509&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=59577868\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190509%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D59577868&d=oAUO7kpDmgkuxlfprI4EYXjCBy0DQDxxpn8JrxrWeYE%3D&h=dd6de511\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190509%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D59577868&h=ed959b5d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190509&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=59577868</a><br />\n內容係總結返成件事既發展<br />\n<br />\n有時就係鐘意蘋果動咁樣<br />\n唔係只post一啲有所謂「名氣」嘅人（片尾有）<br />\n令大家都認識佢地<br />\n我都想大家認識一下呢班英雄<br />\n<br />\n係呢到都想問一下大家<br />\n當年可以聚集到咁多支持勇武抗爭既抗爭者<br />\n係如何形成 點樣聚集到<br />\n<br />\n到底當年肯企出來旺角街頭嘅人<br />\n經歷左呢3年既審判<br />\n係更企硬<br />\n定係又打沉左<br />\n<br />\n到底今次移交逃犯條例<br />\n仲可唔可以聚集到一班支持勇武抗爭嘅人出來<br />\n<br />\n我知我唔係邊個<br />\n但我想同各位道歉<br />\n當年我無出到來<br />\n對唔住大家<br />\n就算呢家知道呢件事達成唔到乜野成效<br />\n比我揀多次<br />\n我會出來<br />\n<br />\n最後 我只想大家<br />\n認識一下片尾嘅各位"},{"pid":"79ee5d10e921dc78bd71882129c7e3265f732a26","tid":1146572,"uid":217098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T15:50:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1d0b1a82e66a0bae18c27324e44b3443b0a80e15","tid":1146572,"uid":66390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T17:03:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3ffdd5a044cdde911b60170a0c93a5317a0cf2c6","tid":1146572,"uid":66390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T17:03:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5b730d2a379122c0865e6ca5ae770b4999e9cc25","tid":1146572,"ui